column5: I 've fished on this lake  many times and have caught at least one musky every time there but for the past two year's I have not caught one only Pike...………..I need to find a new spot to fish...….i'm thinking Lake St Francis...…………..?
Some nice fish in St. Francis
apparently there are some nice ones! That destination has been on my mind...just too far for the one or two day ventures I go on currently
Lake St. Francis has some monsters and would assume decent numbers as I almost catch one every time I'm out there but I'm fishing for bass!
